{"tid":2296404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署方就禤雅達違規一事已完成內部調查 結果為投訴不成立","createTime":"2020-11-22T12:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T16:08:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":359,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b7f89d9b89c1ada95664ec2773c2fd839ed961","tid":2296404,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"前「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林早前被控涉嫌違反「港版國安法」分裂國家等罪名，並被裁定不准保釋，目前正收押於壁屋懲教所候審。前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒引述消息指，一名懲教助理在沒有任何原因下，於昨今兩日（21、22日），強行要求鍾翰林步操逾4小時；據悉該名懲教助理名為禤雅達，早前涉及虐打在囚抗爭者，他於事件曝光後一度休假，惟《蘋果》收到消息指，署方就禤違規一事已完成內部調查，結果為投訴不成立。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回覆指經初步暸解後「並無此事」，又稱對個別公眾人士作出惡意指控予以嚴厲譴責，已就事件展開內部調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201122/CADJ6HWE3RCAHHLOYGKSVMTTDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201122%2FCADJ6HWE3RCAHHLOYGKSVMTTDE%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItTwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=5f279c2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201122%2FCADJ6HWE3RCAHHLOYGKSVMTTDE%2F&h=93425975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201122/CADJ6HWE3RCAHHLOYGKSVMTTDE/</a>"},{"pid":"833a4f25913d16d0825c83d5d639d470ce0c5954","tid":2296404,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb9a4dbf446121ca9a150c69309b9864dc9d901","tid":2296404,"uid":27530,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"你地唔係意外呀化？"},{"pid":"b5241e256331681f31e252d9ba01e2ce6ad6d8e3","tid":2296404,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i